Hey <%= @investor.first_name %>!

<p>
  I'm <a href="http://<%= ENV['MARKETING_DOMAIN'] %>">VCWiz</a>, a tool for founders to discover investors built by Dorm Room Fund and First Round.
  <%= founder @founder %> is using me to reach out to you about potentially funding their company, <%= @company.name %>.
</p>

<%= render partial: 'company' %>

<hr />

<h3>Your Response</h3>

<p>
  Before I can make the intro, I need you to opt-in to receiving intros through VCWiz.
  You will still get the chance to say yes or no to each individual intro request.
</p>

<p>
  <span class="bolder">Click <a href="<%= external_vcwiz_opt_in_url(optin: true, accept: true, token: @request.token) %>">here</a> to opt-in to VCWiz intros, and to accept <%= @founder.name %>'s request.</span><br />
  <span class="bolder">Click <a href="<%= external_vcwiz_opt_in_url(optin: true, accept: false, token: @request.token) %>">here</a> to opt-in, but decline the intro request for <%= @company.name %>.</span><br />
  <span class="bolder">Click <a href="<%= external_vcwiz_opt_in_url(optin: false, accept: false, token: @request.token) %>">here</a> if you'd rather not get intro requests through VCWiz.</span><br />
</p>